CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

December 26, 2006

[Cite as 12/26/2006 Case Announcements, 2006-Ohio-6755.]

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2006-1747. Abrams v. Am. Computer Technology.

Hamilton App. No. C050466, 2006-0hio-4032. This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

It is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
